nodes.text: Frost was a Cathar male Jedi Master serving the Jedi Order and the  Galactic Republic. Frost was stationed on Taris during the Cold War.
Frost was originally set to appear in the  video game Star Wars: The Old Republic but for some unknown reason his character was cut before release. Frost's file can be found on Jedipedia.
